# ⚠️ Generated Files — Do Not Edit

The JSON files in this directory are **generated** by `mix llm_db.build` and will be overwritten.

## How to contribute model data changes

1. Edit or create TOML files under `priv/llm_db/local/<provider>/`
2. Run `mix llm_db.build` to regenerate these JSON files
3. Commit both the TOML changes and the regenerated JSON

See [CONTRIBUTING.md](../../../CONTRIBUTING.md) for full details.
